             was indicted for <rs id="t17980704-4-off11" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980704-4-off11" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980704-4-off11" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980704-4-cd12" type="crimeDate">27th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980704-4-off11 t17980704-4-cd12"></join>, a ewe-sheep, value 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980704-4-victim71" type="victimName">
                     Matthew 
                     Stone
                  <interp inst="t17980704-4-victim71" type="surname" value="Stone"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980704-4-victim71" type="given" value="Matthew"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980704-4-victim71" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980704-4-off11 t17980704-4-victim71"></join>
