                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980704-4-defend69 t17980704-4-punish15"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
